{
  "stem": "24171.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And again, and so somehow the Germans, they went and got a barrel-- a big, big barrel.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then people stood, I don't know, there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And everybody got-- there was a big pile of pots, kind of, cups.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And everybody went in and had water.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when I gathered my cup, I don't know what happened.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The cup drowned, fell out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I stood, already, in this side, between those people which had water, already.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The girls kept on saying to me, my nieces, said Regina, switch in, switch in.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You see, switch in.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I did, and I switched in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As long as my water food were not yet there, in that line for the water, I felt a hand over my neck.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I fell to the ground.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I was naked.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, it was that gravel-- sharp gravel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I got this side, whole was scratched and bloody.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So anyway, that was finished and then we were in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I got lost, about-- about the thing, there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I have to leave that, now, and to tell what happened when my nieces went, and when they came, that the 14-year-olds should stay out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So as the-- from one side, she's supposed to come in-- the SS woman, to-- whatever they would have done, with the 14-year-olds.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I went in the front, at that gate, and that door, and started begging the other girl-- she was a Jewish.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She said-- you know, I said, I have her here, and let me out.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And somehow, maybe, I'll switch her in-- something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And she said, she can't do it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She said, then she say, all right.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You want to be shot?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Go ahead.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she let me out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She let me out, through there.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
